name: Tourafrica
tagline: This is an android version of a tourist app and portal for Africa. The app provides first hand navigation and tour guides to all African tourist sites. This is the first version of TourAfrica App
body:
### Welcome to GDG GULU Github Repositories.
We are a community committed to open source projects and team work is our quest for technological conquest in Africa. Please feel free to post your contributions to our projects.
### Authors and Contributors
Our Lead @Ogwang is the brain behind the app
